oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">press release</=
a>, the <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26666543.2=
70608/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9ydWxlcy9wcm9wb3NlZC8yMDIyL2lhLTU5NTUucGRm/=
607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB50f6bb13" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"item=
scope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !im=
portant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bot=
tom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">proposed rule</a> and the SEC=E2=
=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26666543.2=
70608/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9maWxlcy9pYS01OTU1LWZhY3Qtc2hlZXQucGRm/607f=
07ceef4b8524a319a23cB8834592d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscop=
e" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
